<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <video autoplay loop muted>
          <source src="/public/images/hero-intro.webm" type="video/webm" />
          <source src="/public/images/hero-intro.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <div class="text">
          <div class="subtitle">Coming Soon...</div>

          <div class="title mb-3">Sugar List</div>
          <div class="desc">Luxury dating and much more!</div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="toRegister()">
            Join Now
          </button>
          <div class="learnMore" onclick="scrollToLearnMore()">Learn more</div>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay"></div>
      </section>

      <section class="how-it-works content" id="learnMore">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="title">Find Someone Special</div>
          <div class="sub primary">How it Works?</div>
          <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
              <img src="/public/images/register.svg" alt="register" />
              <div class="title">Register</div>
              <div class="desc">
                Create your profile with just a few details to begin your
                journey towards finding the perfect match.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <img src="/public/images/connect.svg" alt="connect" />
              <div class="title">Connect</div>
              <div class="desc">
                Browse through profiles and connect to those who catch your eye,
                bringing you one step closer to meeting your ideal match.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <img src="/public/images/chat.svg" alt="chat" />
              <div class="title">Interact</div>
              <div class="desc">
                Engage in meaningful chats to discover if there's a true
                connection, helping you determine if it's the perfect match.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="who-we-are content">
        <video autoplay loop muted poster="/public/images/Sequence 01_1.png">
          <source src="/public/images/Sequence 01_1.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="grid">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Who We Are?</div>
              <div class="sub">
                At Sugarlist, we're more than just a dating platformâ€”we're a
                community focused on meaningful connections and empowerment. We
                offer unique features like 1-on-1 video chats to help you build
                authentic relationships. we will provide opportunities to earn
                passive income while connecting with like-minded individuals.
                Additionally, our marketplace will allow users to explore and
                purchase a range of digital and physical erotic products.
                Sugarlist is where connection meets opportunity, all in a safe
                and engaging environment.
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="toRegister()">
                Join Now
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="module_title content">
        <img src="/public/images/module_title.webp" alt="module title image" />
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="title t-light">What's inside Sugar List?</div>
            <div class="desc t-light">Glimpse of the Modules:</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="module_pl content">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="title t-light">Profile List</div>
            <div class="desc t-light">
              At SugarList, we've made it easy for Sugar Daddies and Sugar Babes
              to find each other and connect. Each user has a profile page that
              they can customize with their interests, hobbies, and expectations
              for the arrangement. Using our search and discovery feature, Sugar
              Daddies and Sugar Babes can filter potential matches based on
              location, age, gender, interests, and more.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="single_profile_img">
        <img
          src="/public/images/singlepro.webp"
          width="100%"
          alt="Single profile view"
        />
      </section>

      <section class="modules iShop content">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="grid_2">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Inbuilt Shop</div>
              <div class="desc">
                At SugarList, we've recognized a significant demand for erotic
                products in the market. As part of our platform, we offer an
                inbuilt shop where Sugar Babes can sell their private videos,
                images, and even their worn undergarments, including socks. This
                feature not only generates a passive income for Sugar Babes but
                also keeps users engaged on the platform and provides them with
                everything they need.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <img src="/public/images/ishopp.webp" width="100%" alt="Shop" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="modules chat content">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="grid_2">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Realtime Chat</div>
              <div class="desc">
                SugarList offers a Realtime chat feature that enables Sugar
                Babes and Sugar Daddies to communicate via text. Within the
                chat, Sugar Daddies can send virtual gifts, which generates an
                income for the Sugar Babes. This feature enhances the user
                experience by providing an interactive and engaging platform for
                communication while also allowing Sugar Babes to monetize their
                time spent on the platform.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <img src="/public/images/sChat.webp" alt="chat" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="layout mt-5">
          <div class="grid_2 aend">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Video 1-2-1</div>
              <div class="desc">
                At SugarList, we've created a revolutionary feature that allows
                Sugar Babes to sell their private live streaming shows and earn
                coins in exchange. With the ability to set their own cost per
                minute, this feature has the potential to be a game changer in
                the industry. Sugar Babes can earn a significant income, even
                just by streaming online. This feature provide them with a
                flexible and lucrative way to monetize their content.
              </div>
              <img
                src="/public/images/liveStreamChat.webp"
                style="width: 100% !important"
                alt="live chat"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <img
                src="/public/images/sLiveStrem.webp"
                class="mb-5"
                alt="Live stream"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="modules wallet content">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="grid_2">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="title">Inbuilt wallet</div>
              <div class="desc">
                At SugarList, our inbuilt wallet serves as the central hub for
                our users to manage their purchased coins, earnings, and
                monetization income. Our platform currency is coins, which users
                can exchange fiat for and use to purchase products, send virtual
                gifts, and buy private live streaming from Sugar Babes.
                <br />
                <br />
                Sugar Babes have complete visibility and control over their
                income, as they can manage and convert their coins to fiat and
                withdraw to their bank or PayPal. This feature provides a
                convenient and secure way for Sugar Babes to access and manage
                their earnings on the platform.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <img
                src="/public/images/sWallet1.webp"
                width="100%"
                alt="Wallet"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="join-banner content">
        <div class="layout">
          <div class="col mx-auto">
            <div class="title t-light">Secure one month free membership!</div>
            <div class="desc t-light">
              Register now on our prelaunch phase 1 app and earn a free month of
              membership when we launch the sugarlist.de
            </div>

            <button class="btn mx-auto mt-3 btn-primary" onclick="toRegister()">
              Join Now
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <!-- javascript -->
    <%- include('partials/js') %>
    <script>
      function scrollToLearnMore() {
        document.getElementById("learnMore").scrollIntoView({
          behavior: "smooth",
        });
      }
    </script>
    <!-- javascript end -->
  </body>
</html>
